Bacon Unicorn

This was made by Estelle Weyl, Stacie Hibino and Anna Billstrom for the AT & T HTML5 Mobile Hackathon.

This will geolocate you, and add photos to your location, as a "geo-locator cache game". 

Client: [localhost]/client
location: index.html
server: [localhost/server/
listener for mms: [localhost]/server/receiveMMS.php

To implement:
1. update the client/config.php with AT & T short code, etc.
2. update the server/config.php with apikey/secret/short code

